What do you need to let go of within yourself to make the changes you wish to see?

Do whatever you need to do under this Full Moon so that you can set yourself free to create the life you desire in 2023. 🕊️

You will walk through the darkest of nights right before you see the dawn ✨

These last years have been tough- but they have all shown me the path back to ME. 

I want to gently remind everyone- I am not an overnight success. 

The first 30 (plus) years of my life were woven with intense trauma, deep loss and a lot of redirections. 

Many identities later- I am beginning to see that the intensity of loss I experienced has a place in this world to help others heal theirs. 

For me, The Craft is deeper then manifesting love or a million dollars.

It is a way of life that honors the power that is within us all. 

To go deeper - and guide from within.

You hold all that you wish to ever experience in the palms of your hands. 

Wherever you are at on this journey- know that whatever loss, resistance, grief, hardship you are experiencing- there is an opposite but equal power that lies in you to transform it.
